dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses in Langlade County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Langlade_Addresses_2018.gdb. [Address points represent invididual address locations with permanent improvements some of which have been field verified.Purpose: The address points are used in geocoding valid locations within Langlade County. These are essential for critical functions such as emergency response and dispatch.Maintenance and Update Frequency: Quarterly depending on demand for new or modified addresses.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Langlade County Land Records and Regulations Department
